import React from 'react' import {AiOutlineFolderOpen, AiOutlineEdit, AiOutlineShareAlt, AiOutlineDelete} from 'react-icons/ai' import {RiContactsBookLine, RiFolderUserLine} from 'react-icons/ri' import {MdOpenInNew} from 'react-icons/md' import styles from './ProjectCard.module.css' import { useDispatch, useSelector } from 'react-redux' import { deleteProject } from '../../../store/actions/projectAction' const ProjectCard = ({project}) => { const dispatch = useDispatch() const {auth} = useSelector(state=>state) const deleteHandler = () => { RiContactsBookLine.log(project) dispatch(deleteProject(auth, project._id)) } return (
{project.name}
Author: {project.author.username}
) } export default ProjectCard
